{{vgname|孤岛惊魂6|en=Far Cry 6|cn=孤岛惊魂6|tw=極地戰嚎6}}是一款由[[育碧多伦多|育碧多伦多]]开发并由[[育碧|育碧]]发行在[[Amazon_Luna|Amazon Luna]]、[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]和[[Google_Stadia|Google Stadia]]平台上的[[动作冒险游戏|动作冒险]][[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]，是[[孤岛惊魂系列|孤岛惊魂系列]]的第六部正统作品，原先預期將在2021年2月18日公開發售<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.destructoid.com/stories/here-s-another-quick-look-at-giancarlo-gus-esposito-in-far-cry-6-out-next-february-597193.phtml | title = Here's another quick look at Giancarlo 'Gus' Esposito in Far Cry 6, out next February | first = Chris | last = Carter | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | archive-date = 2021-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210425142335/https://www.destructoid.com/stories/here-s-another-quick-look-at-giancarlo-gus-esposito-in-far-cry-6-out-next-february-597193.phtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但育碧後來在2020年10月29日宣佈因為[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]的關係，將該作推遲到下一財政年度發佈<ref name=Delay>{{cite web | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/far-cry-6-delayed-until-after-march-2021 | title = Far Cry 6 Delayed Until After March 2021 | first = Matt | last = T.M. Kim | date = 2020-10-29 | accessdate = 2020-10-29 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | archive-date = 2021-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210209195046/https://www.ign.com/articles/far-cry-6-delayed-until-after-march-2021 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

遊戲的舞台在虚构加勒比海岛“雅拉”（Yara）上，玩家将操控一名游击队员丹尼·羅哈斯（Dani Rojas），为了推翻雅拉总统安东·卡斯蒂约（{{lang|es|Antón Castillo}}，由[[詹卡洛·埃斯波西托|詹卡洛·埃斯波西托]]飾演）和其兒子迪亞哥（Diego，由{{link-en|安東尼·岡薩雷斯|Anthony Gonzalez (actor)}}飾演）的独裁统治而团结各种力量并为此奋斗。

== 設定 ==
《孤岛惊魂6》是一款[[动作冒险游戏|动作冒险]][[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]，並沿用[[極地戰嚎5|前作]]的臨時槍枝、載具和僱用同仁系統，以及用作推翻殘暴政權的「招募犬牙」（Fangs for Hire）系統<ref name="vg247 announce"/>。

《極地戰嚎6》的故事發生在虛構的加勒比島嶼「雅拉」（Yara）上。該島的靈感來自[[古巴|古巴]]，開發團隊形容該作將會是「極地戰嚎系列中迄今為止最大的[[開放世界|開放世界]]」以及「仿佛時間遭到停止的熱帶天堂」。「雅拉」由綽號「總統」（El Presidente）的[[法西斯|法西斯]]獨裁者安东·卡斯蒂约（{{lang|es|Antón Castillo}}，由[[詹卡洛·埃斯波西托|詹卡洛·埃斯波西托]]飾演）完全掌控，他正引導兒子迪亞哥（Diego，由{{link-en|安東尼·岡薩雷斯|Anthony Gonzalez (actor)}}飾演）成為其繼承者，但後者並未確定自己未來是否會走上父親的老路<ref name="polcharge">{{cite web |last1=Fillari |first1=Alessandro |title=Far Cry 6 Dev Explains The New Politically-Charged Setting |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-6-dev-explains-the-new-politicallycharged-/1100-6479625/ |publisher=GameSpot |accessdate=2020-07-13 |date=2020-07-13 |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714160732/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-6-dev-explains-the-new-politicallycharged-/1100-6479625/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。卡斯蒂略的演員埃斯波西托形容自己的角色「試圖讓人們知道現在需要一位[[強人_(政治)|強而有力的領導人]]」，但此舉卻令國家身陷在革命的泥潭之中<ref name="variety esposito"/>。他續指卡斯蒂略的父親本身便是一位獨裁者，前者掌權後便通過[[鎖國|鎖國]]以及不允許知識份子與[[智慧財產權|智慧財產權]]資源外流等高壓手段，讓人民有能力奪回自己的國家<ref>{{Citation|title=Far Cry 6: Giancarlo Esposit on Who His Villain Anton Is - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/far-cry-6-giancarlo-esposito-on-who-his-villain-anton-is|language=en|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901144847/https://www.ign.com/articles/far-cry-6-giancarlo-esposito-on-who-his-villain-anton-is|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃斯波西托還表示卡斯蒂略正努力地讓迪亞哥有能力承擔自己的職責，並使他真正接受自己將會成為「雅拉」下一位領導人的現實<ref name="variety esposito">{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/giancarlo-esposito-far-cry-6-gus-fring-1234703712/ | title = Giancarlo Esposito on Playing a Gus Fring-esque Dictator in ‘Far Cry 6’ | first = Audrey Cloe | last = Yap | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | archive-date = 2020-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818230022/https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/giancarlo-esposito-far-cry-6-gus-fring-1234703712/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

作中主角是一位試圖令自己的國家恢復到昔日輝煌，在雅拉長大的遊擊兵丹尼·羅哈斯（Dani Rojas），玩家可以在遊戲開始前選擇其性別<ref name="vg247 announce">{{Cite web | url = https://www.vg247.com/2020/07/12/far-cry-6-release-date-trailer/ | title = Far Cry 6 lets you recruit a sausage dog called Chorizo – here’s the trailer and some screens | first = Kirk | last = McKeand | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-date = 2020-07-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200717105615/https://www.vg247.com/2020/07/12/far-cry-6-release-date-trailer/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 開發 ==
在2020年7月首次披露前，《極地戰嚎6》已經進入開發階段近四年，由[[育碧多倫多|育碧多倫多]]操刀<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-07-12-far-cry-6-announced-due-february-2021 | title = Far Cry 6 officially confirmed | first = Tom | last = Phillips | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031065220/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-07-12-far-cry-6-announced-due-february-2021 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{link-en|遊戲敘事設計師|Narrative designer}}納維德·卡瓦利（Navid Khavari）稱開發團隊有研究過去發生的革命，在偶然接觸到諸如[[古巴革命|古巴革命]]等現代遊擊革命的思想，這給了他們很多關於促使玩家角色與專制政權抗爭的想法，也為作中主角丹尼·羅哈斯（Dani Rojas），帶回最近極地戰嚎系列的主角都缺少的必要參與權。卡瓦利還說：「就我們而言，確保主角在這場『革命』中有參與權是必不可少的<ref name="gamespot narrative">{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-6-dev-explains-the-new-setting-of-yara-and/1100-6479625/ | title = Far Cry 6 Dev Explains The New Setting Of Yara, And How Political Revolution Is Core To The Story | first = Alessandro | last = Fillari | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2020-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200713023305/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-6-dev-explains-the-new-setting-of-yara-and/1100-6479625/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>」。以古巴作背景也令遊戲回歸到熱帶環境的設定，也就是早期極地戰嚎系列作品的特色。也因為該國經受長期[[經濟制裁|經濟制裁]]的關係，《極地戰嚎6》的舞台看起來顯得「不合時宜」，街上到處是老式的汽車，使用的武器卻是現代槍械<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/far-cry-6-cuba-yara-tropical-setting-explained | title = Far Cry 6: Why We're Headed Back to a Tropical Island Setting | first = Joe | last = Skrebels | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | archive-date = 2021-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204225200/https://www.ign.com/articles/far-cry-6-cuba-yara-tropical-setting-explained | dead-url = no }}</ref>。卡瓦利曾在古巴逗留一個月，與當地的居民交談，以更好地開發遊戲<ref>{{cite web | url = https://kotaku.com/far-cry-6-is-set-on-an-island-nation-inspired-by-cuba-1844356058 | title = Far Cry 6 Is Set On An Island Nation Inspired By Cuba | first = Zack | last = Zwiezen | date = 2020-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | work = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | archive-date = 2021-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116062406/https://kotaku.com/far-cry-6-is-set-on-an-island-nation-inspired-by-cuba-1844356058 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2020年7月上旬，演員[[詹卡洛·埃斯波西托|詹卡洛·埃斯波西托]]表示自己最近參與了一部「大型電子遊戲」，其中包括配音和[[動作捕捉|動作捕捉]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Breaking Bad's Giancarlo Esposito Is Working On A Big Video Game That He Can't Tell You About|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/breaking-bads-giancarlo-esposito-is-working-on-a-b/1100-6479253/|access-date=2020-07-10|website=GameSpot|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101070654/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/breaking-bads-giancarlo-esposito-is-working-on-a-b/1100-6479253/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久之後，有謠言指出《極地戰嚎6》正在開發，同時也流出了埃斯波西托的角色畫面<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-6-confirmed-with-clip-featuring-breaking-b/1100-6479577/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f | title = Far Cry 6 Confirmed With Clip Featuring Breaking Bad's Giancarlo Esposito | first = Steve | last = Watts | date = 2020-07-10 | accessdate = 2020-07-10 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2021-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210425142308/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/halo-infinite-graphics-will-get-better-and-better-/1100-6480138/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。幾天後，育碧發表公告確認《極地戰嚎6》的存在，並於2020年7月12日在Ubisoft Forward的線上活動正式披露遊戲的預告片<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=July 2020|first=Alex Avard 10|title=Ubisoft acknowledges Far Cry 6 leak in cheeky teaser|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/far-cry-6-leak/|access-date=2020-07-10|website=gamesradar|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101045802/https://www.gamesradar.com/far-cry-6-leak/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此外，{{link-en|安東尼·岡薩雷斯|Anthony Gonzalez (actor)}}則為迪亞哥（Diego）獻聲、提供角色模型和動作捕捉<ref name="vg247 announce"/>。埃斯波西托和岡薩雷斯都是先為《極地戰嚎6》的預告片作動作捕捉和配音，然後再拍攝遊戲的劇情內容，這樣做是因為育碧需要時間創建角色模型<ref name="variety esposito"/>。就埃斯波西托而言，曾為已取消的雙月刊漫畫系列改編電影《{{link-en|老鼠護衛|Mouse Guard}}》的他對角色的動作捕捉方面很感興趣，並曾表示願意在未來接同類型的工作，也對育碧為其創造的角色感滿意<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/far-cry-6-giancarlo-esposito-how-portray-a-villain-audiences-love-hate-1302880 | title = 'Far Cry 6': Giancarlo Esposito on How to Portray a Villain Audiences "Love and Hate" | first1 = Patrick | last1 = Shanley | first2 = Natalie | last2 = Jarvey | date = 2020-07-13 | accessdate = 2020-07-13 | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-date = 2020-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201203082100/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/far-cry-6-giancarlo-esposito-how-portray-a-villain-audiences-love-hate-1302880 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。卡瓦利表示他們已經向埃斯波西托提供角色的背景資料，以令他為遊戲的拍攝做準備。而到了開發會議的時候，卡瓦利發現埃斯波西托已經根據開發團隊發給他的材料做了許多研究，而且還對安東·卡斯蒂略本身展現出驚人的同理心，這是卡瓦利沒想到的<ref name="gamespot narrative"/>。此外，《極地戰嚎6》的配樂由{{le|佩德罗·布朗夫曼|Pedro Bromfman}}負責<ref name="vg247 announce"/>。

